:: Public Holidays
"Jour de l'An"                        public on january 1
"Vendredi saint"                      public religious on easter minus 2 days
"Pâques"                              public religious on easter
"Lundi de Pâques"                     public on easter plus 1 day
"Jour de la Reine (Journée nationale des patriotes)"  public on monday before may 25
"Fête nationale du Québec"    public on june 24
"Fête du Canada"            public on july 1
"Fête du Travail"                     public on first monday in september
"Journée nationale de la vérité et de la réconciliation" public  on ( (year >= 2021) ? [september 30] : noop )
"Action de grâces"                    public on second monday in october
"Jour du Souvenir (Armistice 1918)"   public on november 11
"Jour de Noël"                                public religious on december 25

